	(pipecmd_free): Free cmd->cwd.
	* lib/pipeline.h (pipecmd_chdir): Add prototype.
	* man/Makefile.am (FUNCTIONS): Add pipecmd_chdir.
	* man/libpipeline.3 (Functions to build individual commands):
	Document pipecmd_chdir.
